DISPATCH_PROMPT [merge-supervisor]:

BEAD_ID: workspace-1yb

Refine the hero header overlay in the existing worktree at /app/.worktrees/bd-workspace-1yb/

cd /app/.worktrees/bd-workspace-1yb

## 1. Update src/components/ui/Tag/Tag.astro

Add a `variant` prop with "default" and "dark" styles:

```astro
---
import type { HTMLAttributes } from "astro/types";

interface Props extends HTMLAttributes<"a"> {
  tag: string;
  variant?: "default" | "dark";
}

const { tag, variant = "default", class: className, ...props } = Astro.props;

const variantClasses = {
  default: "bg-gray-light text-gray-dark hover:bg-accent hover:text-white!",
  dark: "bg-white/20 text-white hover:bg-white/30",
};
---

<a
  href={`/tags/${tag}/`}
  class:list={[
    "py-1 px-2 rounded text-sm no-underline",
    variantClasses[variant],
    className,
  ]}
  {...props}
>
  {tag}
</a>
```

## 2. Update src/layouts/BlogPostLayout.astro

Change the hero header overlay section (lines 45-59) to:

```astro
<header class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 backdrop-blur-sm bg-black/25 p-6 xl:p-8 max-w-[400px] rounded-tr-lg">
  <h1 class="md:text-3xl m-0 mb-2 text-white [text-shadow:_0_2px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">{title}</h1>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-300 flex-wrap">
    <FormattedDate date={pubDate} />
    {updatedDate && (
      <span class="italic">
        Updated <FormattedDate date={updatedDate} />
      </span>
    )}
    {tags && tags.length > 0 && (
      <>
        <span class="text-gray-400">|</span>
        {tags.map((t) => <Tag tag={t} variant="dark" />)}
      </>
    )}
  </div>
</header>
```

Key changes from current:
- `backdrop-blur-md` → `backdrop-blur-sm` (less blur)
- `bg-black/40` → `bg-black/25` (less dark)
- Remove `right-0`, add `max-w-[400px] rounded-tr-lg` (not full width)
- `md:text-5xl` → `md:text-3xl` (smaller title)
- Add `[text-shadow:_0_2px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]` to h1 (thick shadow)
- `mb-4` → `mb-2` on h1 (tighter)
- Merge tags and date into single flex row with `|` separator
- Tags use `variant="dark"`
- Remove the separate tags d
